title: Episode 25 - Voice of an Angel
description:
Smug, Holmes, and Duncan pay homage to the end of Trump’s Twitter reply guys, honor the life of Sheldon Adelson, discuss the left’s culpability in misinformation, and cover a new revelation of Weiner.
